{"tid":602572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人性何在】越南血腥活動 獒犬活生生咬死野豬","createTime":"2018-03-23T05:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T11:17:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3169eacb932f6c40549440ef9d0faa2e8d9461","tid":602572,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"即時國際  2018-03-23 00:02:53 HKT\t<br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n越南社交網最近流傳一段短片，片中見到數隻狗圍攻一隻野豬，四周更有數十人圍觀，活動遭動物組織及網民炮轟，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發在周日，片段拍攝於河內西北部一個空地上。片中開始時見到一隻野豬從籠內被放出來，然後一群阿根廷獒犬便撲上去圍攻狂咬野豬，最後野豬慘遭獒犬咬死。獒犬的主人及觀眾在過程中看得興高采烈又不時歡呼，據悉這個活動由一群阿根廷獒犬（Argentine mastiff）愛好者發起。<br />\n<br />\n片段公開後引來各界炮轟，動物專家武玉石（Vu Ngoc Thanh，音譯）形容這個活動「野蠻和不文明」，「人性在哪裡？」。<br />\n<br />\n「Animals Asia」發言人阮心成（Nguyen Tam Thanh，音譯）則表示：「這根本是有心虐待動物，如果事件被忽視，將來肯定會陸續有來。」<br />\n<br />\n警方指涉事活動未有得到許可，目前正調查事件，嘗試找出活動的負責人及參與者身份。"},{"pid":"86cf69de0e635192e8b4a692f6f92166edd62ae4","tid":602572,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180323/57976134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57976134&d=0ukGSjiNL14Cx8Un7%2B1nc0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c1cd015f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57976134&h=7e4046da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180323/57976134</a>"},{"pid":"2872998dd8dce5acea0086031c5f1607e325600c","tid":602572,"uid":90135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:02:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾人種係咁架啦"},{"pid":"c74e5a2d44ea14288fedb70d05ce33b8236b11bd","tid":602572,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連野豬都要愛護"},{"pid":"66eecfbf609bc366d776aca0bd960b322bd10cb1","tid":602572,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"&quot;片段公開後引來各界炮轟&quot;<br />\n<br />\n你有你鬧，佢有佢繼續，有咩用"},{"pid":"6c6b6a1bf8b032f43f9786d251795e669a5029c2","tid":602572,"uid":24282,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"豬又唔係人類朋友<br />\n<br />\n是但啦😑唔知佢會唔會整到啲狗狗呢"},{"pid":"c619baff76b7216fc51d9f1157ae2a36ec595540","tid":602572,"uid":93266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"係越南講人性同係大陸講人性既結果都係一樣"},{"pid":"b1a2df5e104479357de51f068766a973c2b3a103","tid":602572,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"792a93e1464b5ba071d6d387b0976534198da696","tid":602572,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"點解係美國用槍掃射無人屌？"},{"pid":"44660d7f8aca63628cc4250d3b1f9c13f7f84265","tid":602572,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b269061c4f884982d0c543bdbd552908c505e7","tid":602572,"uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"低等嘅豬係狗狗嘅食物黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205a0601ced533b8d8bc838a1c70cac17cc3eb73","tid":602572,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7ede49af609abab65af71746c740dd06a0b38a8","tid":602572,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"017c92b9c2ba06e12211c32bb4d52c99c33181e6","tid":602572,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}